{"tid":1309471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地上月新增人民幣貸款1.66萬億元","createTime":"2019-07-12T08:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T08:25:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f93bf4dc6ed55c6c43807722f5617d3fa2dea7a8","tid":1309471,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:16:50.000Z","msg":"內地上月新增人民幣貸款略低於預期，不過社會融資規模升急。人民銀行公布，上月新增人民幣貸款有1.66萬億元人民幣，按月上升近41%，不過略低於預期的1.7萬億元。上月廣義貨幣供應量(M2)按年增長8.5%，低於預期的8.6%。不過社會融資規模有2.26萬億元，按月急升61%，亦大幅高於預期。"},{"pid":"587264eeffa10a0f8916d0cd6acca035974e5455","tid":1309471,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:17:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8581e94714c10c28e4c64beede6e79deace8cd1","tid":1309471,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:21:40.000Z","msg":"WFC china data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685586baabd6adc3d0087eca214a1dc1a8f2caf1","tid":1309471,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:21:42.000Z","msg":"利申戇鳩<br />\n即係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481d3e972823310fefe747c69c09bf1703f24411","tid":1309471,"uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"銀行無錢咪印囉"},{"pid":"0d527380b4f3435a89534db1bc9894fb103eef51","tid":1309471,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"481d3e972823310fefe747c69c09bf1703f24411","tid":1309471,"uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"銀行無錢咪印囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"家陣貨幣電子化<br />\n墨水都慳番"}]}